  <brief_title>Effect of Liraglutide on Weight and Appetite in Obese Subjects With Type 2 Diabetes</brief_title>
  <official_title>NNC 90-1170 Mechanism of Action: A Single-centre, Randomised, Double-blind, Parallel-group, Placebo-controlled Trial Evaluating the Effect of NNC 90-1170 on Weight and Appetite in Obese Subjects With Type 2 Diabetes</official_title>
