  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is conducted in Europe. The aim of the trial is to investigate the effect of NNC
      90-1170 (liraglutide) on weight and appetite in obese subjects with type 2 diabetes treated
      with diet and/or sulphonylurea or repaglinide.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
